    "Figure 1 LLM, its baseline version, and other leading LLMs, demonstrating efficient management of computational resources.",
    "Despite the integration of external knowledge bases, Mistral LLM demonstrates an admirable balance between maintaining quick response times and efficient resource utilization, comparing favorably to its baseline and even improving upon certain metrics when compared to other LLMs.",
